Parameters.Name: VIDEO ENCODER CONFIGURATION – H.264 RESOLUTION (ALL RESOLUTIONS)

Test.Name: All VEC doesn't support H264
Test.Description: All VEC doesn't support H264 Check that thete is Warning in the test tool log Check that test tool will try to set jpeg for the first, middle anf last VECs DUT behaviour is incorrect: it is imposible to modify VEC to required encoding

Test.Name: One VEC supports H.264
Test.Description: The second VEC supports H.264 Check that test tool will try to find/careate profile for the second VEC Check that test tool will not test the other VECs

Test.Name: More than 3 VECs support H.264
Test.Description: The 2nd VEC supports H.264 The 3rd VEC supports H.264 The 4th VEC supports H.264 The 5th VEC supports H.264 Check that test tool will try to find/careate profile for three VECs: 2, 4 and 5. Check that test tool will not test the other VECs

Test.Name: All VECs don't support H264: the last VEC is changed to H264
Test.Description: All VECs don't support H264 Check that thete is Warning in the test tool log Check that test tool will try to set H264 for the first, middle anf last VECs DUT behaviour is correct: the last VEC will changed to the required encoding
